# Privacy Policy

**MIS Archive** does not collect, store, or share any personal data from users.

The app does not require user registration or login, and it does not track user activity.

No personal information is collected through the use of this application.

The app does not use third-party analytics, advertising services, or tracking tools.

All content and interactions occur locally on the user’s device.

